{"name":"task","description":"Generic table for tasks that need to be performed, used as a parent table for many other task-based tables like incidents and changes.","summary":"In ServiceNow, the `task` object is a fundamental component used to manage and track various types of work items within the platform. Here's a summary of the `task` object:\n\n### Key Features:\n1. **Work Item Management**: The `task` object serves as a base for different types of work items, such as incidents, problems, changes, and service requests.\n2. **Customization**: It can be extended to create custom applications and workflows tailored to specific business needs.\n3. **Fields and Attributes**: The `task` object includes a variety of fields to capture details such as status, priority, assignment group, assigned to, due date, and description.\n4. **Relationships**: It can be linked to other records and objects within ServiceNow, such as users, configuration items (CIs), and other tasks.\n5. **Workflow Automation**: Tasks can be integrated with workflows to automate processes, send notifications, and escalate issues as needed.\n6. **Reporting and Analytics**: Data from the `task` object can be used to generate reports and dashboards, providing insights into workload, performance, and trends.\n\n### Common Use Cases:\n- **Incident Management**: Tracking and resolving issues that impact services.\n- **Problem Management**: Identifying and addressing the root causes of incidents.\n- **Change Management**: Managing changes to services and infrastructure.\n- **Service Requests**: Fulfilling user requests for services or resources.\n- **Custom Applications**: Creating specialized workflows and applications to meet unique business requirements.\n\n### Example Fields:\n- **Number**: Unique identifier for the task.\n- **Short Description**: Brief summary of the task.\n- **Description**: Detailed information about the task.\n- **State**: Current status of the task (e.g., New, In Progress, Resolved).\n- **Priority**: Importance and urgency of the task.\n- **Assignment Group**: Team or group responsible for the task.\n- **Assigned To**: Individual responsible for the task.\n- **Due Date**: Deadline for completing the task.\n\n### Integration:\nThe `task` object can be integrated with other ServiceNow modules and external systems to streamline workflows, improve efficiency, and enhance service delivery.\n\n","attributes":[{"name":"parent","type":"reference"},{"name":"made_sla","type":"boolean"},{"name":"watch_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"upon_reject","type":"string"},{"name":"sys_updated_on","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"task_effective_number","type":"string"},{"name":"approval_history","type":"journal"},{"name":"skills","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"number","type":"string"},{"name":"sys_updated_by","type":"string"},{"name":"opened_by","type":"reference"},{"name":"user_input","type":"user_input"},{"name":"sys_created_on","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"sys_domain","type":"domain_id"},{"name":"state","type":"integer"},{"name":"sys_created_by","type":"string"},{"name":"route_reason","type":"integer"},{"name":"knowledge","type":"boolean"},{"name":"order","type":"integer"},{"name":"closed_at","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"cmdb_ci","type":"reference"},{"name":"delivery_plan","type":"reference"},{"name":"impact","type":"integer"},{"name":"contract","type":"reference"},{"name":"active","type":"boolean"},{"name":"work_notes_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"business_service","type":"reference"},{"name":"priority","type":"integer"},{"name":"sys_domain_path","type":"domain_path"},{"name":"time_worked","type":"timer"},{"name":"expected_start","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"opened_at","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"business_duration","type":"glide_duration"},{"name":"group_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"work_end","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"approval_set","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"work_notes","type":"journal_input"},{"name